sentences: During the SBSTA opening plenary on Monday, 1 June, the UNFCCC Secretariat introduced this item (UNFCCC/SBSTA/2015/INF.3 and Corr.1) outlining the Secretariat§s engagement with other international organizations and stakeholders.
Parties agreed that Chair Wojtal would consult with interested parties.
During its closing plenary, the SBSTA adopted conclusions.
